<br>
But anyway, in guilds mages can Call of Hero, which is needed at high level, that's the main thing they offer, other than standard battle.<br>
<br>
In groups, you're similar to wizards, with some variations... nuke as much as you can without taking agro (waiting till the mob is lower on life works well), use the right pet for the occasion, and summon up fun toys like arrows for the puller and all that.<br>
<br>
