<br>
In my 2 &amp;1/2 years playing everquest I have seen quite a few High elf magicians in their 50's on other servers &amp; I've yet to hear one say 'I wish I had made another race for this class'.<br>
<br>
Especially this being a roleplaying server, go with what you want to do, regardless of whether it's min/maxed to the extreme.<br>
